scaf - simple auto cpu frequencer
=================================
Work In Porgress (ONLY FOR TESTING)

sacf it's a daemon that monitors the cpu N number of seconds and simply tweak
governors and decided whether to use turbo boost or not.

Usage
-----

	sacf [-cvltT]


